And on behalf of the
National Book Festival Board,

00:00:29.350 --> 00:00:31.780
The Library of Congress, I
want to welcome everybody

00:00:31.780 --> 00:00:35.510
to this extraordinary event, so
thank you very much for coming.

00:00:35.510 --> 00:00:41.610
