from some very distinguished authors

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:09.790
and then I think you'll
be quite pleased to hear

00:11:09.790 --> 00:11:12.000
from their extraordinary comments.

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:22.510
Ladies and gentlemen,
Kwame Alexander.

