after his exploration

00:23:35.830 --> 00:23:39.180
in Latin America Humboldt
returned to Europe,

00:23:39.180 --> 00:23:44.200
but he did a little detour and he
stopped at Philadelphia and then

00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:47.020
