there were two carriages.

00:24:30.630 --> 00:24:34.720
The two drivers of the
carriages were absolute drunk

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:40.140
by the time the dinner was done
and decided to race back to D.C.

00:24:40.140 --> 00:24:42.790
So every time one of the
carriage drivers tried

00:24:42.790 --> 00:24:45.580
