to The Library

00:26:08.290 --> 00:26:13.270
of Congress there were quite a few
Humboldt books in that collection.

00:26:13.270 --> 00:26:18.460 position:56%
So my book, The Invention of Nature,
is my attempt to find Humboldt

00:26:18.460 --> 00:26:20.930
