say what we say,

00:47:04.360 --> 00:47:07.170
and publish what we
write for other people.

00:47:07.170 --> 00:47:10.500
And then for these
works to be treated

00:47:10.500 --> 00:47:20.930
as treasure this is what
is noble about our country.

