native people, backs of women,

00:48:44.060 --> 00:48:49.260
all of that is all part
of what we write about.

00:48:49.260 --> 00:48:55.460
And all that is part of the
extraordinary complexity

00:48:55.460 --> 00:48:57.310
that we find ourselves in.

